$interpreted: Royal Infantry: Oh no!
Sione: A Royal Infantry uniform!?
Sione: Who are you? Why did you assault me?
Royal Infantry: ...None of your business!
Sione: Did you open the cages and release the beasts?
Sione: What is your purpose?
Royal Infantry: Like I said, none of your business!
Royal Infantry: Damnit, get out of my way! Arrggghhh!
Female Noble: No!
Sione: So you ARE the culprit! How dare a lowly kidnapper like you parade as Royal Infantry!
Sione: For the honor of the Royal Infantry, I shall apprehend you!
Female Noble: No, it's a misunderstanding! It is not what you think it is!
Royal Infantry: It's useless, she won't listen! Worst case scenario, I'll put my life on the line!
Female Noble: But.....!
Royal Infantry: I'd rather die than see you marry someone that you have absolutely no interest in!
Sione: Errrrr... what are you guys talking about?
Dylan: I'll take care of her. You guys leave, now!
Royal Infantry: Colonel Levon! How did you...
Dylan: I already know everything about you two.
Royal Infantry: ...Sorry. I didn't want to drag you into this mess, sir...
Dylan: Nonsense! I said before, my men are like family to me. We're in this mess together.
Sione: Let me go!
Dylan: Now stop wasting time and get moving!
Royal Infantry: Thank you, sir!
